name: Sonya Kennell-Green
text: Great food! Great customer service. Our food was ready in no time and the dining area was very neat and well maintained.

name: Tammy Blazer
text: Great Place to Eat Will Come Back. Tammy Blazer

name: Loria Smith
text: Nice atmosphere and nice employees had a birthday party there and it was very nice

name: Kevin Wright
text: Excellent service and food is the greatest I've ever tasted from a pizza hut.

name: Don Rohr
text: The food was good, the employees were very helpful and the location was clean and quiet.

text: im in love with dat pizza

text: They were out of a lot of things. No salad bar, no personal pan pizzas. Limited menu.
